{"id":133,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":133,"title":"D&C 129","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 129"],[".studyIntro",["i","Instructions given by Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Nauvoo, Illinois, February 9, 1843, making known three grand keys by which the correct nature of ministering angels and spirits may be distinguished."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.1-3"},"1–3"],", There are both resurrected and spirit bodies in heaven;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.4-9"},"4–9"],", Keys are given whereby messengers from beyond the veil may be identified."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.1","order":"06.05.129.16048"},["b","1"],"There are two kinds of beings in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"heaven"],", namely:",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Angels"],", who are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"resurrected"],"personages, having",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"bodies"],"of flesh and bones—"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.2","order":"06.05.129.16049"},["b","2"],"For instance, Jesus said:",["i","Handle me and see, for a spirit hath not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"flesh"],"and bones, as ye see me have."]],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.3","order":"06.05.129.16050"},["b","3"],"Secondly: the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"spirits"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"just"],"men made",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"perfect"],", they who are not resurrected, but inherit the same glory."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.4","order":"06.05.129.16051"},["b","4"],"When a messenger comes saying he has a message from God, offer him your hand and request him to shake hands with you."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.5","order":"06.05.129.16052"},["b","5"],"If he be an angel he will do so, and you will feel his hand."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.6","order":"06.05.129.16053"},["b","6"],"If he be the spirit of a just man made perfect he will come in his glory; for that is the only way he can appear—"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.7","order":"06.05.129.16054"},["b","7"],"Ask him to shake hands with you, but he will not move, because it is contrary to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"order"],"of heaven for a just man to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"deceive"],"; but he will still deliver his message."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.8","order":"06.05.129.16055"},["b","8"],"If it be the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"devil"],"as an angel of light, when you ask him to shake hands he will offer you his hand, and you will not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"feel"],"anything; you may therefore detect him."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.9","order":"06.05.129.16056"},["b","9"],"These are three grand",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"keys"],"whereby you may know whether any administration is from God."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.1a","order":"06.05.129.16057"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heaven"},"TG Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.1b","order":"06.05.129.16059"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.1c","order":"06.05.129.16061"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.1d","order":"06.05.129.16063"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.52.52-53"},"Matt. 27:52 (52–53)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.2a","order":"06.05.129.16065"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/24.39"},"Luke 24:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.3a","order":"06.05.129.16067"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirit-body"},"TG Spirit Body"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-disembodied"},"Spirits, Disembodied"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.3b","order":"06.05.129.16069"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/6.9"},"Gen. 6:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.23"},"Heb. 12:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.69"},"D&C 76:69"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.3c","order":"06.05.129.16071"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-potential-to-become-like-heavenly-father"},"TG Man, Potential to Become like Heavenly Father"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.7a","order":"06.05.129.16073"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/order"},"TG Order"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.7b","order":"06.05.129.16075"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deceit"},"TG Deceit"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lying"},"Lying"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.8a","order":"06.05.129.16077"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.14"},"2 Cor. 11:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.9"},"2 Ne. 9:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.8b","order":"06.05.129.16079"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/131.8.7-8"},"D&C 131:8 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.9a","order":"06.05.129.16081"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/4.1.1-6"},"1 Jn. 4:1 (1–6)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/discernment-spiritual"},"TG Discernment, Spiritual"],"."]]}
